OL,3,CMan charged with murder of 'beautiful
OL,4,Cand kind' mother-of-two
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fa mother-of-two in Llanelli.
OL,9,FThe body of Sophie Evans, 30, was
OL,10,Ffound in a house on Bigyn Road, in
OL,11,FLlanelli, Carmarthenshire, on 5 July.
OL,13,FA murder enquiry was launched, with
OL,14,FRichard Jones, of Y Rhodfa in Burry
OL,15,FPort, arrested later that day.
OL,17,FOfficers have since charged the 49-
OL,18,Fyear-old, who was known to Sophie,
OL,19,Fwith her murder.
