OL,6,FJones has been remanded into custody
OL,7,Fand will appear at Llanelli
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Friday, 12 July.
OL,10,FA Dyfed-Powys Police spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with Sophie's
OL,12,Ffamily at this time, and they continue
OL,13,Fto receive support from specialist
OL,14,Fofficers.
OL,16,F"The investigation team is grateful
OL,17,Ffor the support of the community while
OL,18,Fenquiries have been carried out."
